snippet.textDisplay: Initially I thought it was a man singing. After listening to top 20 coke studio india songs, I have no desire to visit the rest. Don't get me wrong, I came here expecting some great music. However, I found the music and sound engineering below par. I have no intention to draw comparisons here. Visit coke studio pak and see and feel the difference by yourselves. I still hope there would be good music coming from india.
